=Description=

"Commons catalysts from across the country working on a wide variety of initiatives—from food security to climate justice to water governance—came together to connect and collaborate; build shared knowledge, tools, and materials; and grow and strengthen the commons movement. The CSL’s design grew out of our belief that by connecting commons-based efforts, we can build movement momentum—and expand the potential impact of our work as commoners."


